          <p>
            Sketch an accurate,
            labeled graph of <m>s</m> on the axes provided in <xref ref="F-1-3-Act2">Figure</xref>.
            You should be able to do this without using computing technology.
          </p>
        </statement>
        <hint/>
        <answer/>
